Why I chose MIS as my major is because I have been around technology all my life and I love to learn how it works and how I can use it to my beneift. Also for the business aspect I found that the concepts of business come easy to me since my family owns a small business and I have been helping out since I was little. So I figured that MIS would be a good major for me since it combines two things that have been an important to me for most of my life.
